cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper deals with natural language understanding and reasoning, which are core topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves computational linguistics (cs.CL) as it focuses on understanding textual corpus. The use of norms and causal reasoning involves machine learning (cs.LG) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the application of this system to accident analysis involves computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
